OL,4,Carsonist
OL,6,FA man who started and stoked multiple
OL,7,Ffires during rioting at a hotel
OL,8,Fhousing asylum seekers has been jailed.
OL,10,FScott Greenwood, of Tingle Bridge
OL,11,FLane, Hemingfield, Barnsley, was
OL,12,Ffilmed setting fire to wood fence
OL,13,Fpanelling in the car park of the
OL,14,FHoliday Inn Express in Manvers,
OL,15,FRotherham, during unrest on 4 August.
OL,17,FThe 34-year-old was also recorded
OL,18,Ftaking bunches of dried grass and
OL,19,Fadding them to a fire on the grassland
OL,20,Fsurrounding the hotel.
