OL,4,Carsonist
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to violent disorder
OL,7,Fand arson with intent to endanger life
OL,8,Fat Sheffield Crown Court and was
OL,9,Fjailed for six years, with an extended
OL,10,Flicence period of three years.
OL,12,FGreenwood was among hundreds of people
OL,13,Fwho gathered outside the hotel, where
OL,14,Faround 200 asylum seekers were
OL,15,Fstaying, in one of a series of anti-
OL,16,Fimmigration protests after the murders
OL,17,Fof three girls in Southport.
OL,19,FThe hotel had its windows smashed and
OL,20,Fmissiles including wood, glass bottles
OL,21,Fand beer cans were thrown at police.
