OL,6,FOfficers were forced to retreat before
OL,7,Fa group of rioters got into the hotel.
OL,8,FA bin was pushed against the building
OL,9,Fand set alight.
OL,11,FSouth Yorkshire Police said 75 people
OL,12,Fhave been convicted and sentenced to a
OL,13,Fcombined total of 167 years in jail
OL,14,Ffollowing the incident in Rotherham.
